orm-of-euthanasia%2F&d=Nfsz5E3m9Y1rIgqi3P%2FNwHadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=cb0a33e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thevintagenews.com/2017/01/23/in-ancient-rome-suicide-was-allowed-as-a-form-of-euthanasia/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T22:09:42.000Z","msg":"Ancient Greece and Rome both had pretty lenient attitudes towards suicide. Ancient Roman civilization had a somewhat progressive approach which in some way resembled euthanasia. In Rome, suicide was not considered a crime or a sin against gods, and in some cases, it was deemed justifiable and pragmatic."},{"pid":"d536afd44a64f4b8ff741095ab4230696e49775b","tid":961137,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T22:10:28.000Z","msg":"屌你有書有文獻　當我尻吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc00cbbbc44ddcd9a3e4a4ce247ed51d6fee793","tid":961137,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4003c53c316ff1e000813453882ac6459b7afc13","tid":961137,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0018c767a520b286f4aee239ab77cddf3b26748","tid":961137,"uid":42374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T20:17:13.000Z","msg":"古希臘無可能會<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T22:02:26.000Z","msg":"古希臘直情民眾安樂死添喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thevintagenews.com/2017/01/23/in-ancient-rome-suicide-was-allowed-as-a-form-of-euthanasia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thevintagenews.com%2F2017%2F01%2F23%2Fin-ancient-rome-suicide-was-allowed-as-a-form-of-euthanasia%2F&d=Nfsz5E3m9Y1rIgqi3P%2FNwHadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=cb0a33e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thevintagenews.com/2017/01/23/in-ancient-rome-suicide-was-allowed-as-a-form-of-euthanasia/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:35:40.000Z","msg":"呢個講緊古羅馬喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0d9668d2b950a0d2d7d8faff36af69572c1b1b","tid":961137,"uid":42374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:49:52.000Z","msg":"古希臘文明對於自殺行為不同於基督教與伊斯蘭教，自殺是可以允許，也可以理解的行為。如果一個人自殺前，能夠向國家申請，說明理由，並且得到議會的批准，那麼自殺就是合法的。只有在個人沒有得到國家批准時，自殺才是非法的。這個時候，自殺的人因為做了對國家不忠誠的事情而要受到凌辱,比如不能夠享受正常的榮譽和葬禮，而且自殺者的一雙手還要被砍下來另埋他處，因為正是這雙罪惡的手結束了他自己的生命，因此，這雙手不能夠享受與他的屍體同等的待遇。"},{"pid":"989be5a91b293364db551114e3673f1bcacec885","tid":961137,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9auN5rr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9auN5rr.jpg&h=0576fc38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bff0756fa3a88c6f87fdfb6a2865343c60e05070","tid":961137,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abc00cbbbc44ddcd9a3e4a4ce247ed51d6fee793","tid":961137,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4003c53c316ff1e000813453882ac6459b7afc13","tid":961137,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0018c767a520b286f4aee239ab77cddf3b26748","tid":961137,"uid":42374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T20:17:13.000Z","msg":"古希臘無可能會<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T22:02:26.000Z","msg":"古希臘直情民眾安樂死添喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thevintagenews.com/2017/01/23/in-ancient-rome-suicide-was-allowed-as-a-form-of-euthanasia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thevintagenews.com%2F2017%2F01%2F23%2Fin-ancient-rome-suicide-was-allowed-as-a-form-of-euthanasia%2F&d=Nfsz5E3m9Y1rIgqi3P%2FNwHadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=cb0a33e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thevintagenews.com/2017/01/23/in-ancient-rome-suicide-was-allowed-as-a-form-of-euthanasia/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:35:40.000Z",